## Limitations

This report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023. The housing market is subject to rapid changes influenced by economic policies, global events, and local regulations, which may not be fully captured in this analysis. Additionally, the focus on U.S. housing markets, particularly California, may not reflect global housing trends. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more current analysis.